        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed text-center fade-in delay-1">
          RESSS began as a weekly savings society in Gaibandha in 2014. Since then, we have expanded across a range of 
          community-focused investment opportunities: seasonal Rabi crop financing, agro-farming projects, land-backed 
          rice cultivation loans, and rental investments such as shop leases. Our model blends careful local knowledge 
          with transparent processes to increase members' capital and weekly savings sustainably. 
        </p>
